      • twistMove

        static short[][] twistMove
        Move table for the twists of the corners. Keeps for each combination of corners orientation and move the new corner orientation after executing the move.
        twist < 2187 in phase 1
        twist = 0 in phase 2

      • flipMove

        static short[][] flipMove
        Move table for the flips of the edges. Keeps for each combination of corners orientation and move the new corner orientation after executing the move.
        flip < 2048 in phase 1
        flip = 0 in phase 2

      • parityMove

        static short[][] parityMove
        Parity of the corner permutation. This is the same as the parity for the edge permutation of a valid cube. parity has values 0 and 1

      • FRtoBR_Move

        static short[][] FRtoBR_Move
        Move table for the four UD-slice edges FR, FL, BL and BR
        FRtoBRMove < 11880 in phase 1
        FRtoBRMove < 24 in phase 2 (since they are already in the slice)
        FRtoBRMove = 0 for solved cube

      • URFtoDLF_Move

        static short[][] URFtoDLF_Move
        Move table for permutation of six corners. The positions of the DBL and DRB corners are determined by the parity.
        URFtoDLF < 20160 in both phases (1 and 2)
        URFtoDLF = 0 for solved cube

      • URtoDF_Move

        static short[][] URtoDF_Move
        Move table for the permutation of six U-face and D-face edges in phase2. The positions of the DL and DB edges are determined by the parity.
        URtoDF < 665280 in phase 1
        URtoDF < 20160 in phase 2
        URtoDF = 0 for solved cube

      • URtoUL_Move

        static short[][] URtoUL_Move
        Move table for the three edges UR,UF and UL in phase1.

      • UBtoDF_Move

        static short[][] UBtoDF_Move
        Move table for the three edges UB,DR and DF in phase1.

      • MergeURtoULandUBtoDF

        static short[][] MergeURtoULandUBtoDF
        Table to merge the coordinates of the UR,UF,UL and UB,DR,DF edges at the beginning of phase2

      • Slice_URFtoDLF_Parity_Prun

        static byte[] Slice_URFtoDLF_Parity_Prun
        Pruning table for the permutation of the corners and the UD-slice edges in phase2. The pruning table entries give a lower estimation for the number of moves to reach the solved cube.

      • Slice_URtoDF_Parity_Prun

        static byte[] Slice_URtoDF_Parity_Prun
        Pruning table for the permutation of the edges in phase2. The pruning table entries give a lower estimation for the number of moves to reach the solved cube.

      • Slice_Twist_Prun

        static byte[] Slice_Twist_Prun
        Pruning table for the twist of the corners and the position (not permutation) of the UD-slice edges in phase1. The pruning table entries give a lower estimation for the number of moves to reach the H-subgroup.

      • Slice_Flip_Prun

        static byte[] Slice_Flip_Prun
        Pruning table for the flip of the edges and the position (not permutation) of the UD-slice edges in phase1. The pruning table entries give a lower estimation for the number of moves to reach the H-subgroup.
